   before comparison, so case or region-subtag mismatches ("EN" vs
   "en-GB") can't cause a false negative either.

Recommendation summary: Task 1D's merge itself should NOT be blocked —
its own scope, tests, and citations are correct. Findings 1 and 2 are
new (not raised by tester) and belong to 1D's owner as a small follow-up
